ğŸ“ˆ Results & Insights

Key findings from the analysis:

ğŸ“Œ Finance and Healthcare sectors are consistently the most targeted.

ğŸ“Œ A major spike in attacks was observed in 2020â€“2021, coinciding with remote work adoption.

ğŸ“Œ Ransomware and Phishing dominate as common attack vectors.

